  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink94-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">varaiviṭai vaittup pirinta talaimakaṉ mīḷkiṉṟāṉ colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink94">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>maḷḷa raṉṉa taṭaṅkōṭ ṭerumai</l>
          <l>makaḷi raṉṉa tuṇaiyoṭu vatiyu</l>
          <l>niḻaṉmuti rilañcip paḻaṉat tatuvē</l>
          <l>kaḻaṉit tāmarai malaruṅ</l>
          <l>kaviṉpeṟu cuṭarnuta ṟantai yūrē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> The town of her father– </l>
          <l> that girl with a beautiful glowing forehead</l>
          <l> that blooms [like] a lotus in the tank – </l>
          <l> is in the paddy fields with Ilañci trees surrounded by shade,</l>
          <l> where the broad-horned buffalos that look like warriors </l>
          <l> stay close to [their] females that resemble women. </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
